## ğŸ”µ 1. Basic CSS Syntax

```css
selector {
  property: value;
}
```

---

## ğŸ”µ 2. Adding CSS to HTML

**Inline:**

```html
<p style="color: red;">Red Text</p>
```

**Internal:**

```html
<style>
  p { color: blue; }
</style>
```

**External:**

```html
<link rel="stylesheet" href="style.css" />
```

---

## ğŸ”µ 3. CSS Selectors

```css
/* Element selector */
p { color: green; }

/* Class selector */
.box { padding: 10px; }

/* ID selector */
#header { font-size: 20px; }
```

---

## ğŸ”µ 4. CSS Box Model

